cs.CY, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CL

This paper deals with the analysis of content in Wikipedia, which falls under the category of computational social science (cs.CY). The paper also involves automatic content analysis, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The study also involves analyzing biases in the coverage of natural disasters, which can be considered a social issue (cs.SI) and falls under the broader category of sustainable development (cs.SD).
